com.cisco.mscviewer - package com.cisco.mscviewer
Contains classes and packages for MSCViewer, a tool for visualization and analysis of sequence diagram charts (see Wikipedia}.
com.cisco.mscviewer.expression - package com.cisco.mscviewer.expression
Contains classes to implement an expression parsing engine for expression entered in the filtering and search GUI elements.
com.cisco.mscviewer.graph - package com.cisco.mscviewer.graph
Contains classes for creation of a graph used to compute a topological sorting of Event in the data model.
com.cisco.mscviewer.gui - package com.cisco.mscviewer.gui
Contains classes for the GUI of MSCViewer.

Contains classes for loading/saving MSCViewer data model from and to files.
com.cisco.mscviewer.model - package com.cisco.mscviewer.model
Contains classes representing MSCViewer view and data model.
com.cisco.mscviewer.script - package com.cisco.mscviewer.script
Contains classes supporting Python scripting in MSCViewer
com.cisco.mscviewer.tree - package com.cisco.mscviewer.tree
Contains classes for implementation of an Augmented Tree used to store Interactions.
